General.Name: Precomp Solutions AB Series B
General.Description: Precomp Solutions AB (publ) manufactures and supplies precision components to the automotive and manufacturing industries in Europe. It presses components in various types of material using fineblanking technology; produces deep drawned components using stamping technology; offers finishing and assembly solutions; and designs and manufactures tools. Precomp Solutions AB (publ) was founded in 1956 and is headquartered in Ulricehamn, Sweden.
